parameters:
There's a pool of clear water here. This looks like a good
place to wash off the dirt on my body.
Shall I wash off the dirt from my body?

\n<Man a>"You guys! Ah, what a relief! I never thought I'd meet
someone at a time like this!"
\n<Roselitte>"What about you? What are you doing in a place like this?"

\n<Man a>"We were out hunting. Then, a bunch of monsters appeared,
and we couldn't make it back to town... Oh! More
importantly, please look at my partner!"

Behind the man who was speaking, another man was sitting.
His expression was twisted in agony, and he was dragging a
leg soaked in black blood.

\n<Man a>"We were trying to make it back to town somehow, but we were
just attacked by a monster! Please, help us!"
\n<Ameria>"It's okay! I can heal you! Just stay still, okay?"

\n<Man b>"Ah... It's like a lie. Such a terrible injury, healed in an
instant..."

\n<Man a>"Amazing! A miracle! To think we'd meet a healer in a place
like this!"

\n<Man b>"...Thank you. You saved me. It's not much, but please
accept this."
\n<Roselitte>"Shall we accompany you to the town?"

\n<Man b>"No... It's okay. The town is just around the corner. You're
out here at such a time too. You must have some urgent
business, right?"

\n<Man a>"Now that the injury is healed, there's no need to worry if
we've made it this far! This area is like our backyard!"

\n<Man a>"Let's go, partner! Let's hurry back and share our
incredible adventure story!"

\n<Man a>"Miss! Thank you so much for your help! We're lucky to have
met a healer like you!"

\n<Ameria>"Ah, thank you. But please be careful on your way.
Hallelujah~"
